	<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en">Customer</h1>
	
	<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
		<div id="siteSub" class="noprint">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>
		<div id="contentSub"></div>
		
		
		
		<div id="jump-to-nav"></div>
		<a class="mw-jump-link" href="#mw-head">Jump to navigation</a>
		<a class="mw-jump-link" href="#p-search">Jump to search</a>
		<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">For the Raheem DeVaughn song, see <a href="/wiki/Customer_(song)" title="Customer (song)">Customer (song)</a>.</div>
<div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">"Clientele" redirects here. For the British rock band, see <a href="/wiki/The_Clientele" title="The Clientele">The Clientele</a>.</div>
<table class="box-Confusing plainlinks metadata ambox ambox-style ambox-confusing" role="presentation"><tbody><tr><td class="mbox-image"><div style="width:52px"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/f/f2/Edit-clear.svg/40px-Edit-clear.svg.png" decoding="async" width="40" height="40" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/f/f2/Edit-clear.svg/60px-Edit-clear.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/f/f2/Edit-clear.svg/80px-Edit-clear.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="48" data-file-height="48" /></div></td><td class="mbox-text"><div class="mbox-text-span">This article <b>may be <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Vagueness" title="Wikipedia:Vagueness">confusing or unclear</a> to readers</b>.<span class="hide-when-compact"> Please help us <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Please_clarify" title="Wikipedia:Please clarify">clarify the article</a>. There might be a discussion about this on <a href="/wiki/Talk:Customer" title="Talk:Customer">the talk page</a>.</span>  <small class="date-container"><i>(<span class="date">August 2016</span>)</i></small><small class="hide-when-compact"><i> (<a href="/wiki/Help:Maintenance_template_removal" title="Help:Maintenance template removal">Learn how and when to remove this template message</a>)</i></small></div></td></tr></tbody></table>
<p>In <a href="/wiki/Sales" title="Sales">sales</a>, <a href="/wiki/Commerce" title="Commerce">commerce</a> and <a href="/wiki/Economics" title="Economics">economics</a>, a <b>customer</b> (sometimes known as a <b><a href="https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/client" class="extiw" title="wikt:client">client</a></b>, <b><a href="/wiki/Buyer" title="Buyer">buyer</a></b>, or <b><a href="/wiki/Purchasing" title="Purchasing">purchaser</a></b>) is the recipient of a <a href="/wiki/Good_(economics)" class="mw-redirect" title="Good (economics)">good</a>, <a href="/wiki/Service_(economics)" title="Service (economics)">service</a>, <a href="/wiki/Product_(business)" title="Product (business)">product</a> or an <a href="/wiki/Intellectual_property" title="Intellectual property">idea</a> - obtained from a <a href="/wiki/Seller" class="mw-redirect" title="Seller">seller</a>, <a href="/wiki/Vendor" title="Vendor">vendor</a>, or <a href="/wiki/Distribution_(business)" class="mw-redirect" title="Distribution (business)">supplier</a> via a <a href="/wiki/Financial_transaction" title="Financial transaction">financial transaction</a> or <a href="/wiki/Exchange_(economics)" class="mw-redirect" title="Exchange (economics)">exchange</a> for <a href="/wiki/Money" title="Money">money</a> or some  other valuable <a href="/wiki/Consideration" title="Consideration">consideration</a>.<sup id="cite_ref-FOOTNOTEReizenstein2004119_1-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-FOOTNOTEReizenstein2004119-1">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-FOOTNOTEKendall20073_2-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-FOOTNOTEKendall20073-2">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>
</p>
<div id="toc" class="toc"><input type="checkbox" role="button" id="toctogglecheckbox" class="toctogglecheckbox" style="display:none" /><div class="toctitle" lang="en" dir="ltr"><h2>Contents</h2><span class="toctogglespan"><label class="toctogglelabel" for="toctogglecheckbox"></label></span></div>
